{"lemma":"بُسْتانِ","slug":"بُسْتانِ","root":"ب.س.ت","root_slug":"ب-س-ت","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-س-ت","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2508"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8F%D8%B3%D9%92%D8%AA%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"garden"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"orchard"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Persian بوستان (bostân)."},"ipa":["/bus.taːn/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2508","headword_ar":"بُسْتَانٌ","root":"bsA^","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[accord. to its etymology (which will be explained below) and to general modern usage,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A garden of sweet-scented flowers and trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but accord. to the Arabic Lexicons,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garden such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~ap","text_ar":"جَنَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walled garden, such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hadiyqap","text_ar":"حَدِيقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palm-trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in a poem of El-Aashà: (TA:) said by Fr to be an Arabic word; (Msb, TA;) but this is denied by IDrd: (TA:) and said by some to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruwmiY~","text_ar":"رُومِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or Greek]: (Msb:) [but correctly] it is an arabicized word, from [the Persian]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buwsotaAnN","text_ar":"بُوسْتَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[bóstán]; (K, [in which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n","text_ar":"ن"},{"kind":"text","text":"is regarded as a radical letter,] Shifá el-Ghaleel, MF,) meaning “taking odour, or fragrance,” or, as some say, “a place where odour, or fragrance, collects, or is collected:” (Shifá el-Ghaleel, MF:) its composition from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bw","text_ar":"بو"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"stAn","text_ar":"ستان"},{"kind":"text","text":"requires the former meaning to be assigned to it: (TA:) [or rather it signifies “a place of odour, or fragrance:”] afterwards applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"basaAtiynu","text_ar":"بَسَاتِينُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"basaAtuwna","text_ar":"بَسَاتُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayaATiynu","text_ar":"شَيَاطِينُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayaATuwna","text_ar":"شَيَاطُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","M","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}